short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Addon to sync the current opened google sheet with Sukhiba backend

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This addons enable syncing your catalog in google spreadsheet to Sukhiba backend.
Steps:
- First Link your google sheet in https://lite.sukhiba.com
- Then One click sync on this addon will enable you to sync the spreadsheet to sukhiba.
